  "text": "Our meta-analysis has several strengths. It was planned according to the PRISMA guidelines, registered at PROS-PERO and performed according to the Cochrane methodology. A broad search strategy was used and a broad spectrum of studies was included, not only large EGDT trials. We further applied the clinical fact that most critically ill patients are not treated by advanced hemodynamic protocols [CITATION_1] and investigated the results of studies where the controls were treated according to usual care or with simple hemodynamic protocols based on CVP, MAP or lactate or a combination of those parameters.",
